OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few light showers
OL,7,Fpossible this evening. Becoming
OL,8,Flargely dry with variable cloud and
OL,9,Foccasional clear spells overnight.
OL,10,FChance of a few isolated light
OL,11,Fshowers. Breezy and mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FDry with bright or occasional
OL,14,Fsunny spells throughout the day. Cloud
OL,15,Fincreasing to bring some outbreaks of
OL,16,Flight showery rain by the evening.
OL,17,FFeeling warm in sunshine. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
