OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,6,Fdry with bright or sunny spells
OL,7,FSaturday and Sunday. Cloudier on
OL,8,FMonday with a few coastal showers,
OL,9,Fthese possibly spreading inland.
OL,10,FFeeling cooler, especially along
OL,11,Fwindward coastal districts.
